PHASE 4: VERIFICATION & TESTING
======================================================================

Step 4.1: Test from Server Computer
-----------------------------------
1. Install and run Store Parts on the server
2. Configure database connection to: localhost or 127.0.0.1
3. Login with admin/admin
4. Add a test entry
5. Verify it appears in Show Data

Step 4.2: Test from Client Computer
-----------------------------------
1. Install and run Store Parts on a client PC
2. Configure database to server IP: 192.168.1.100
3. Login with admin/admin
4. Verify you can see the entry created from server
5. Add another entry
6. Go back to server, verify the new entry appears

Step 4.3: Test Multi-User Access
--------------------------------
1. Have 2-3 users logged in simultaneously (different PCs)
2. One user adds an entry
3. Other users click "Refresh"
4. All users should see the new entry

Step 4.4: Test Parts Usage
--------------------------
1. Click "Parts Usage"
2. Select a part from the grid
3. Fill in Machine, Person, Quantity
4. Click "Record Usage"
5. Verify usage appears in history

Step 4.5: Test Dashboard
------------------------
1. Click "Dashboard"
2. Verify charts and reports load
3. Check Usage History tab
4. Export a report to CSV

