- Stop MySQL: net stop MySQL80
- Check status: services.msc → MySQL80
- Open firewall: wf.msc
- MySQL CLI: mysql -u root -p

CONNECTION STRING FORMAT:
Server=192.168.1.100;Port=3306;Database=MainDB;Uid=storeparts;Pwd=StoreParts@123;

